==Swedish==
===Noun===
'''schack'''

#[[chess]]; a game of [[strategy]] fir two players. 
#[[check]]; a situation in which the king is directly threatened by enemy pieces

===Interjection===
'''schack'''

#[[check]]; a claim used in [[chess]] to notify the opponent that his/her [[king]] is threatened.

